{"tid":294091,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手求屌] 五日四夜 大阪行程","createTime":"2017-06-22T16:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T08:38:40.000Z","uid":10968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13885f179d5e6699f63b2a637f400b682a1f7ce9","tid":294091,"uid":10968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:11:21.000Z","msg":"酒店住新大阪附近<br />\n食野好多都心齋橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有咩推薦 係返京都神戶奈良食都得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係好識plan 求指點<br />\nday 4 好空 有咩好行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有邊日係好chur? <br />\n同埋想知行程次序會唔會好無腦？<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 :<br />\n(大阪)<br />\n大阪城公園&gt;心齋橋 食LUNCH&gt;美國村 <br />\n&gt;海游館 &gt;心齋橋 食DINNER<br />\n&gt;梅田空中庭園展望台 <br />\n <br />\nDay 2:<br />\n(京都)<br />\n貴船神社&gt;地主神社&gt;食lunch<br />\n&gt;石塀小路 &gt; YEN 山公園 (八阪神社) &gt; 衹園<br />\n&gt;衹園新橋 &gt; 花見小路&gt;食dinner返大阪<br />\n <br />\nDAY3:<br />\n奈良市&gt;奈良公園&gt;食lunch&gt;稻荷 &gt;千本鳥居<br />\n&gt;寺田町 食飯 &gt;通天閣  <br />\n <br />\nDay 4:<br />\n姬路城&gt;神戶塔<br />\n <br />\nDay 5 :<br />\n心齋橋 食野<br />\nRinku Premium outlet  <br />\n關西空港 走人"},{"pid":"6e5b7fb986dfe73ff3f128871d6544498b78bf9c","tid":294091,"uid":10968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T16:24:48.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5c0172b81da365deaad35cbf4f80312cacec85","tid":294091,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"第四日姫路可用jr 1 day pass"},{"pid":"ac11be74e4665b68faad99659b70eebd6493bf4d","tid":294091,"uid":43819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T08:04:40.000Z","msg":"第一日應該大阪城-》海遊館-》美國村-》心齋橋"},{"pid":"767f50250977ae9b8889fa5da7c469bb6159b70e","tid":294091,"uid":6